    "translations": {
      "en": {
        "summary": "The Prophet Muhammad (SAWW), narrated through Imam al-Rida (AS) from his forefathers, warns that a Muslim must never scheme or deceive, as Gabriel (AS) confirmed that scheming and deception lead to Hellfire. This prophetic tradition emphasizes that deceit is fundamentally incompatible with Islamic faith.",
